Louis van Gaal wants Danny Ings to form a central part of Manchester United rebuilding this summer .
High-placed sources at Old Trafford have confirmed their interest in a player who is also being strongly pursued by Liverpool .
The futures of Robin Van Persie and Radamel Falcao are uncertain and Van Gaal has put the 22-year-old Englishman on his list of targets .
Louis van Gaal is a fan of Ings in the Premier League .